com.googlecode.aluminumproject.cli.commands.aludoc

Class AluDoc

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.aluminumproject.cli.Command
      • com.googlecode.aluminumproject.cli.commands.aludoc.AluDoc

  • public class AluDoc
extends Command
    Generates library documentation.

    The aludoc command accepts the following options:

    • The location option (--location): where the documentation will be generated to - the default location is the current directory;
    • The exclude option (-x or --exclude): adds a library to the list of libraries for which no documentation will be generated.
